latestIgtvVideos.title: Open letter to my sister on her wedding
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Didi So now that you have got married I have got some questions and some things to tell you
Who will yell at me ? Who will fight for the TV’s Remote ? Who will flick my t shirts and wear them as night dress ?
Who will tell me to stay away from certain people ? Who will save me from mom’s anger the next time I get in trouble ?

You are going to a different city, how will you hold me tight when I need you at 2am?
Who will hold me together on the nights when I need you to tell me that ‘It’s okay’

Didi, I have grown up with you. Not a day goes by until we fight for something super silly, but to tell you the truth you are the most precious human being I know 

You are like my survival kit. From telling about cool music to putting foundation when I am looking dull, I don’t know where I would be if it weren’t for you.
It scares me to think of the time when I will walk into your room and find it empty.

You’re a wife now. And you will be an exceptional wife. I love you so much. I really can’t express how proud I am of you. You were the most beautiful bride I’ve ever seen, full of grace.
I wish you a lifetime of happiness, because that is exactly what you deserve Didi.
Have a great married life and remember, for me, you are always going to be the go to person ... for life!♥️
@sonukhabiya @nishithkc 
Thanks @simranbalarjain for this beautiful highlights of the whole wedding. #sohitjodi
